{"tid":2398721,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國泰容許商務或頭等艙乘客除罩瞓覺    員工炮轟漠視播疫風險","createTime":"2021-02-07T14:06:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T06:02:15.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"25875f14b43f9922fc67a95b73f383b7edce96c5","tid":2398721,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T14:06:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/pgMqRi0r3kwgtU3FkiUIbQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS41Mzg0NjE1Mzg0NjE1/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/piSwYA9kMiAVZCkVJrnz7A--~B/aD01NTc7dz03ODA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/onccinstantnews.com/99018ca86c7c136b918c4b5f527f5574\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FpgMqRi0r3kwgtU3FkiUIbQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS41Mzg0NjE1Mzg0NjE1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FpiSwYA9kMiAVZCkVJrnz7A--~B%2FaD01NTc7dz03ODA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F99018ca86c7c136b918c4b5f527f5574&h=cf9c6246&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因管理不善而在全球最佳航空公司排名跌出三甲的國泰航空，容許商務或頭等艙乘客除口罩，員工轟漠視播疫風險！本港第四波疫情嚴峻，港府近日再收緊機組人員檢疫措施，冀能堵截傳播鏈，惟國泰竟反其道而行，近日發出新指引，當中列明商務或頭等艙乘客平躺時可脫下口罩。有員工批評資方無視疫情，更可能引來鄰座乘客投訴，斥做法令員工難做；工會亦擔憂措施惹來爆疫風險，促國泰交代豁免戴口罩的原因。<br />\n<br />\n國泰前日（5日）向機組人員發出內部通告，指所有乘客均須佩戴口罩，並列明多項可獲豁免戴口罩的情形，當中包括「當乘客於商務或頭等艙平躺」，15分鐘內的飲食或服藥時間等。有空中服務員批評，做法增加播疫風險，同時亦可能惹來投訴，斥國泰漠視員工健康。<br />\n<br />\n民航工會會長張樞宏指出，新指引下乘客可脫下口罩，不少機組人員擔心工作時或與乘客近距離接觸，期間不慎染疫，表明不認同有關措施。他又提到，國泰未有公開有關原因，相信有可能是「為咗方便乘客」，促國泰交代。<br />\n<br />\n國泰表示，有關額外指引旨在幫助機組人員更加了解豁免佩戴口罩的情況，而頭等及商務艙的座位距離較寬躺，並有間隔，在平躺睡覺時可獲豁免。國泰又指，機艙內採用的高效微粒子空氣過濾系統，可過濾逾99.999%的塵埃微粒及污染物，如病毒和細菌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/dGK2MrfGWqjI0bL61Y9TvQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEwNDA-/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/YGSOde4bAcVN4a9bFniUwQ--~B/aD04NDU7dz03ODA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/onccinstantnews.com/9f9dc853975a5fbdd55418bd3c1b82f9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FdGK2MrfGWqjI0bL61Y9TvQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEwNDA-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FYGSOde4bAcVN4a9bFniUwQ--~B%2FaD04NDU7dz03ODA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F9f9dc853975a5fbdd55418bd3c1b82f9&h=39f81a87&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fccd91f943862ce0da02aae2a70f77775f10c87b","tid":2398721,"uid":78785,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T14:07:54.000Z","msg":"お客様は神様"},{"pid":"86c25fc15dbbe51b961a5d361ad48974f5d8016c","tid":2398721,"uid":224533,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T14:11:42.000Z","msg":"商務頭等客就係皇帝<br />\n叫你奶就奶"},{"pid":"9f9c3cb5e214707608ad0e3cb929dc9fd0183de7","tid":2398721,"uid":185492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T14:13:56.000Z","msg":"應該拍醒d乘客，提佢地帶番個罩<br />\n無限loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b677a5a548e2c7b9bcce083631722e88a899b75","tid":2398721,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f9c3cb5e214707608ad0e3cb929dc9fd0183de7","tid":2398721,"uid":185492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T14:13:56.000Z","msg":"應該拍醒d乘客，提佢地帶番個罩<br />\n無限loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T14:18:31.000Z","msg":"頭等乘客：空姐, 我無罩戴呀！借你個罩比我？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"969d389a1391a8f584f61fb650eb44725cd41987","tid":2398721,"uid":134182,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T14:18:35.000Z","msg":"訓覺都要戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c68fa46d35efb5ce77c8a74a2a410334fbb0c83","tid":2398721,"uid":8410,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"