br />\n民航工會會長張樞宏指出，新指引下乘客可脫下口罩，不少機組人員擔心工作時或與乘客近距離接觸，期間不慎染疫，表明不認同有關措施。他又提到，國泰未有公開有關原因，相信有可能是「為咗方便乘客」，促國泰交代。<br />\n<br />\n國泰表示，有關額外指引旨在幫助機組人員更加了解豁免佩戴口罩的情況，而頭等及商務艙的座位距離較寬躺，並有間隔，在平躺睡覺時可獲豁免。國泰又指，機艙內採用的高效微粒子空氣過濾系統，可過濾逾99.999%的塵埃微粒及污染物，如病毒和細菌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/dGK2MrfGWqjI0bL61Y9TvQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEwNDA-/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/YGSOde4bAcVN4a9bFniUwQ--~B/aD04NDU7dz03ODA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/onccinstantnews.com/9f9dc853975a5fbdd55418bd3c1b82f9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FdGK2MrfGWqjI0bL61Y9TvQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEwNDA-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FYGSOde4bAcVN4a9bFniUwQ--~B%2FaD04NDU7dz03ODA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F9f9dc853975a5fbdd55418bd3c1b82f9&h=39f81a87&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T04:59:06.000Z","msg":"就黎頭等躺下時可以裸睡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46998409df664b0fe11e979b8c81a3444e0fec4f","tid":2398721,"uid":10503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"155cccb53b0b743d905a9ee3cfc9cd59926b383e","tid":2398721,"uid":131157,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T03:15:01.000Z","msg":"係香港成班低等賤民仲係度玩防疫姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T05:01:03.000Z","msg":"真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日日撚封窮撚區<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b112c2b065fbc33a628bb7b02af2a7b860363d","tid":2398721,"uid":75765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T05:06:01.000Z","msg":"要著生化衣先有用, 普通口